name: qada
body:
### Welcome to Qt Abstract Desktop Application project web site.
Please, check out the last version of software by shell command:

```
$ git clone https://github.com/stansage/qada
$ cd qada
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout -b stable v0.0.1
```

### Future reading 
See the README.md file or ask the author. Good luck!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
